hree classes, sharply in contrast to the models obtained by the bottom-up\napproach, the spacetime is already geodesically complete, and no additional\nextensions are needed in both sides of the transition surface. In particular,\nidentical multiple black hole and white hole structures do not exist.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Jun 2022 19:39:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Dec 2022 05:22:33 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 23 Dec 2022 04:23:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-26"}
