k and the task at hand.\nWe empirically validate the value of each of these layers separately with\nbenchmark datasets for graph classification. We also perform preliminary\nstudies on the use of CT-Layer for homophilic and heterophilic node\nclassification tasks. DiffWire brings together the learnability of commute\ntimes to related definitions of curvature, opening the door to creating more\nexpressive MPNNs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Jun 2022 08:22:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 27 Sep 2022 10:28:10 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 30 Nov 2022 19:11:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-07"}
